Feb 1
Release Notes
added RSI details
Shorts: The bot checks yesterday's Daily RSI. If it was above 70 (Overbought), it confirms the stock is extended. If the stock then "Gaps Down" today, the bot treats this as a high-probability reversal and allows the trade.

Longs: It checks if yesterday's Daily RSI was below 30 (Oversold). If the stock then "Gaps Up" today, it signals a "snap back" rally.
